works.description:
Italian fashion and leather goods label  
Gucci is celebrating its 90th anniversary this year, and to mark the  
occasion, they are releasing the 1921 Collection this June. Christened  
after the year in which Guccio Gucci founded the Florentine House, the new  
collection features an exclusive range of men’s and women’s ready to wear  
and accessories. One of the highlights from the new range is the Gucci 1921  
watch collection.
